cast.overview: At a 1962 College, Dean Vernon Wormer is determined to expel the entire Delta Tau Chi Fraternity, but those troublemakers have other plans for him.
cast.title: Animal House

details.biography: Eliza Roberts was born as Eliza Rayfiel. She is a casting director and actress, known for National Lampoon's Animal House (1978), Doctor Who (1996) and Lois & Clark: The New Adventures of Superman (1993). She has been married to Eric Roberts since August 16, 1992. She was previously married to James Simons.
details.name: Eliza Roberts
